{"tid":776230,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"十一月打算自己去沖繩","createTime":"2018-08-11T22:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T16:31:21.000Z","uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c321298a5c50bb7d5af6277f0e261bbb0eb301","tid":776230,"uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:48:51.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴打 如果自己想去沖繩又唔識渣車 <br />\n你地覺得去唔去好<br />\n如果唔去 去邊好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f483770ba56f7ae0dcc73f66c2c257990d545e","tid":776230,"uid":34630,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T22:49:55.000Z","msg":"唔楂車咪撚去"},{"pid":"0938c99bb074335159dff6a295f19dff60c29409","tid":776230,"uid":60887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T23:48:59.000Z","msg":"如果唔追景點,去學潛水嘅話唔揸車都無問題<br />\n3日潛水,每日都去到傍晚左右完,食個夜晚周圍行吓或者返酒店hea吓就一日<br />\n淨返日子咪去返一兩個景點,食吓啲好嘢<br />\n我上次係咁過,覺得幾滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45f244356126862f6c99d6cd29cd1679f624a09","tid":776230,"uid":185229,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"同意#2#3 <br />\n唔揸車真係局限好大"},{"pid":"ec531e80cfd5d145bae319d2c1b56b7888411f46","tid":776230,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:27:47.000Z","msg":"沖繩有啲day tour可以報，有巴士帶你周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69370e0e7eada749aebd87a4d40d2c4eb3245925","tid":776230,"uid":129664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"沖繩一日觀光巴士資料；<br />\n<a href=\"http://okinawa.letsgojp.com/archives/16962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fokinawa.letsgojp.com%2Farchives%2F16962%2F&d=OPdEuTM8pvrXw7khawfK%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e21b4a1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://okinawa.letsgojp.com/archives/16962/</a>"},{"pid":"08285267873a1bc8cbaae1f219f2ddb20633ada9","tid":776230,"uid":155414,"like":0,"