Z","msg":"自己一個會悶居多<br />\n<br />\n你無車牌每個景點要搭車都幾麻煩<br />\n<br />\n你唔揸車享受唔到沖繩既特色"},{"pid":"c0fcce0b64f70cdd2625d17494737e6b8b0f45c1","tid":776230,"uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46e58b14b1dccf0086a65345336ef519d847bed0","tid":776230,"uid":147569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade79ec43c9b476087a45927f9995d001e1ef79d","tid":776230,"uid":155414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aba6ad2bd203f55667581d416e081789cbf285","tid":776230,"uid":147569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"福岡同東京一樣咁多人<br />\n<br />\n睇你自己想去咩景點啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"我就係想去沖繩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"自己一個會悶居多<br />\n<br />\n你無車牌每個景點要搭車都幾麻煩<br />\n<br />\n你唔揸車享受唔到沖繩既特色"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05169b10eca90da0b59416f31b36e167cd93fe5d","tid":776230,"uid":55982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"而家join day tour bus都方便嘅 但就鴨仔團 同埋有啲路線會逼9你去摘菠蘿 好19<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n那霸嗰邊基本上冇乜大問題 有單軌<br />\n但去名護嗰啲真係遠到仆街<br />\n我上年冇車同男朋友去 淨係搭車去萬座毛 搭咗兩粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果去埋水族館應該要四粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋啲巴士班次勁疏 一miss咗就要等成粒鐘"},{"pid":"68120c5c47a7d143e4568bb7dd166523ff7d98a7","tid":776230,"uid":196590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"其實沖繩好易玩 想去景點可以join day tour <br />\n想hea下國際通個到都有好多餐廳食下野行下咁"},{"pid":"b7c1f30991d22d41b77eaa7cf67e90c6faff05c5","tid":776230,"uid":184546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"如果有車牌 但考完之後雪左2年 係咪渣車都好危險<br />\n1個人租車好似好唔抵wor 定有電單車租"},{"pid":"17eb3110cad9d7c851534100aca236ed8cc2db96","tid":776230,"uid":26056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:18:41.000Z","msg":"睇你目的係咩 如果係想追景點就一定係揸車 純休閒想轉下環境9fing絕對冇問題 <br />\n<br />\n自己去過一個星期 無揸車 其實市內景點悠閒玩可以玩到3-4日 首里城美術館瀨長島etc 仲未計shopping <br />\n<br />\n個陣join咗一日day tour去古宇利島水族館美國村 仲有個唔知咩海中公園 冇去菠蘿園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再搵日自己搭巴士去睇玉泉洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係煩啲一定要睇好班次夾時間 但做好基本資料搜集就可以了<br />\n<br />\n至於福岡我去過又唔覺特別多大陸人 反而多韓國人 至於香港人就周圍都多避唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eac13d6db0b9574dd2e7876ea92c4ec3ef6e8a","tid":776230,"uid":110207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T22:45:09.000Z","msg":"預咗好多時間坐巴士先好唔渣車去"},{"pid":"d7380ed3c3d5e83cb039176793e633d3940f437f","tid":776230,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69370e0e7eada749aebd87a4d40d2c4eb3245925","tid":776230,"uid":129664,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"沖繩一日觀光巴士資料；<br />\n<a href=\"http://okinawa.letsgojp.com/archives/16962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fokinawa.letsgojp.com%2Farchives%2F16962%2F&d=OPdEuTM8pvrXw7khawfK%2BNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=e21b4a1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://okinawa.letsgojp.com/archives/16962/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}